    <title type="html"><![CDATA[New Blogging Setup]]></title>
    <link href="http://calumhalcrow.com/blog/2014/01/26/new-blogging-setup/"/>
    <updated>2014-01-26T04:14:00+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://calumhalcrow.com/blog/2014/01/26/new-blogging-setup</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Part of my forward looking plans have been to migrate <a href="http://calumhalcrow.com">calumhalcrow.com</a>
onto a static blogging platform, therefore having more control over the code that drives it.</p>

<!-- more -->


<p>I decided to use <a href="http://octopress.org">Octopress</a> (with the <a href="https://github.com/macjasp/cleanpress">CleanPress</a> theme)
hosted on <a href="http://pages.github.com">Github Pages</a>. Such a setup gives me a static blogging engine, hosted for free,
with full control over my site yet with almost embarrassingly minimal setup work involved.</p>

<p>And this is it.</p>
]]></content>
